---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
const lang = 'zh';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`${lang === 'zh' ? '关于' : 'About'} | Hans Cao Photograph`}
  description="About Hans Cao and this photography archive."
>
  <SiteHeader lang={lang} />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{lang === 'zh' ? '关于' : 'About'}</h1>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-zinc-600">
      {
        lang === 'zh' ? (
          <>
            <p>我是 Hans Cao，这里是我的长期摄影档案。网站以城市、街头与自然为主线，持续整理我历年的影像作品。</p>
            <p>这个站点使用 Astro + TailwindCSS 构建，内容由 Sanity 统一管理，部署在 Vercel。后续新增照片将通过 Sanity 后台直接发布。</p>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <p>I am Hans Cao, and this site is my long-term photography archive. It follows city, street, and nature themes while collecting work from different years.</p>
            <p>This site is built with Astro + TailwindCSS, uses Sanity for content management, and is deployed on Vercel. New photographs are published through the Sanity studio.</p>
          </>
        )
      }
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
